    "Geometry and steel profiles for openseespy/steel_bridge.py (3D, 6-DOF OpenSees model).",
    "End-panel top nodes (LT0, LT6, RT0, RT6) and their members are omitted: no end top chords, verticals, cross-beams, or lateral braces; interior top network remains from LT1/RT1 inward.",
    "Pratt diagonals pivot at bottom-chord element 3 (LB2–LB3): label i≤3 uses LBi–LT(i−1) (LB0–LT1 at support); i>3 uses LBi–LT(i+1) except LB6–LT5; LB1/LB5 verticals only. Mirrored on right truss (RB0–RT1, RB2–RT1, RB3–RT2, RB4–RT5, RB6–RT5).",
    "Main truss and deck transfer members use the 15x15x3 angle steel profile by rule.",
    "Pratt diagonals and lateral bracing use the 15x3 steel flat bar profile by rule.",
    "Bolted joints and load cells are represented as design metadata; a future solver still needs connection stiffness and sensor response models."
  ]
